---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="YouTube | Log8">
  <main class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto p-8">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-brand-primary text-center mb-8">YouTube</h1>
    <p class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 text-lg">성장과 기록을 통해 가치를 공유하는 개발 블로그입니다.</p>

    <section class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-6">Sponge Duk</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- Sponge Duk Latest Episode Embed -->
        <div class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 md:col-span-2">
           <iframe
             src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/8Lq06pG_s_o"
             frameborder="0"
             allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
             allowfullscreen
             class="w-full h-full rounded-lg shadow-md">
           </iframe>
        </div>
        <!-- Sponge Duk Description -->
         <div class="flex flex-col justify-center md:col-span-1">
             <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-primary mb-4">Latest from Sponge Duk</h3>
             <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">AI 개발 여정과 실전 문제 해결 노하우를 담은 스펀지덕의 최신 기술 인사이트를 만나보세요.</p>
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@sponge-duck" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">채널 방문하기 &rarr;</a>
         </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <hr class="my-12">

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-6">Lucky Dukky</h2>
       <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
         <!-- Lucky Dukky Latest Episode Embed -->
        <div class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 md:col-span-2">
           <iframe
             src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/_zS1hzQVIxY"
             frameborder="0"
             allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
             allowfullscreen
             class="w-full h-full rounded-lg shadow-md">
           </iframe>
        </div>
         <!-- Lucky Dukky Description -->
          <div class="flex flex-col justify-center md:col-span-1">
             <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-brand-primary mb-4">Latest from Lucky Dukky</h3>
             <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">일상 속 AI 활용 팁, 생산성 향상 아이디어, 그리고 개발자 김덕환의 솔직한 이야기들을 럭키덕키 채널에서 확인하세요.</p>
              <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Luckyducky-official" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:underline font-medium">채널 방문하기 &rarr;</a>
         </div>
       </div>
    </section>

    <!-- YouTube 구독 섹션 -->
    <section class="mt-16 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-8">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-primary mb-4">YouTube에서 더 많은 콘텐츠를 만나보세요</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">개발 여정과 일상을 공유하는 다양한 영상들을 확인해보세요.</p>
        <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@sponge-duck" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
             class="bg-red-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors duration-200 font-medium">
            Sponge Duk 구독
          </a>
          <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@Luckyducky-official" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" 
             class="bg-red-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors duration-200 font-medium">
            Lucky Dukky 구독
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>